creator: Outdooractive GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Lower Austria is a land of unlimited opportunities when it comes to excursions and vacations. Unwind in the great outdoors; explore art and culture in museums, abbeys, castles and fortresses; and enjoy hot spring resorts. Lower Austria has more than 250 attractions for you to discover on outings. They include Wirtshauskultur restaurants and inns, businesses covered by the Niederösterreich-CARD, TOP excursion destinations plus Lower Austrian gardens and nature parks.
This app with over 1,500 tours (hiking, cycling, mountain biking…) is an ideal companion to help you plan your tours from home or to guide you locally. The map is available online and can also be downloaded. That means the tours stored in it can be retrieved at any time.
All tours have detailed tour information, including length, cumulative elevation gain in meters, duration, difficulty, plus a thorough description featuring pictures, tour route on the map and an elevation profile.
The content of the Lower Austria Guide app is made available by the Lower Austria tourist destinations, Danube in Lower Austria, Mostviertel, Waldviertel, Weinviertel, Vienna Woods and Vienna Alps.


An important note:
Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

title: Lower Austria

creator: Outdooractive AG
descriptionHtml:
Lower Austria, the land of unlimited excursions and vacation opportunities. Relaxing in nature, exploring art and culture in museums, monasteries, castles and palaces, soothing thermal spas and excursion attractions are all to be discovered in Lower Austria. Included are the establishments of the inn culture, the Lower Austria CARD, top excursion destinations, gardens and nature parks of Lower Austria.

Lower Austria Guide -> Tour Guide
The app "Niederösterreich-Guide" is a digital companion, a tour guide. Anyone who wants to experience and hike Lower Austria will quickly find their personal favorite routes in this app - from long-distance hikes and top cycling routes to family-friendly pilgrimage trails and mountain bike routes for beginners and advanced riders. Around 2,000 Lower Austrian tours for every taste are waiting to be discovered. This app is an ideal support for tour planning from home and as a guide on site.

The map is available online, can also be downloaded and saved tours can thus always be called up. All tours have detailed information about the tour incl. length, altitude meters, duration, difficulty, additionally a detailed description incl. pictures, a tour course in the map and an altitude profile. The content of the Lower Austria app is provided by the Lower Austrian tourism destinations, Danube Lower Austria, Mostviertel, Waldviertel, Weinviertel, Vienna Woods and Vienna Alps.

All rights to access that you grant within the scope of this app are default settings of the technology company Outdooractive AG. You are welcome to contact the developers if you have any questions: service@outdooractive.com
